      "date": "2012-05-11 03:49:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nHello Chris,\n\nThe \"hostname\" in the following codes also need to be changed to \"hostname -s\":\n\ntest-framework.sh:141:    export HOSTNAME=${HOSTNAME:-`hostname`}\n\ntest-framework.sh:1079:        \"vmstat 1 > $TESTLOG_PREFIX.$TESTNAME.vmstat.\\\\\\$(hostname).log \\\n\nrun_IOR.sh:9:LOG=$TESTLOG_PREFIX.$(basename $0 .sh)_stdout.$(hostname).log\n\nrun_dbench.sh:9:LOG=$TESTLOG_PREFIX.$(basename $0 .sh)_stdout.$(hostname).log\n\nrun_dd.sh:9:LOG=$TESTLOG_PREFIX.$(basename $0 .sh)_stdout.$(hostname).log\n\nrun_iozone.sh:9:LOG=$TESTLOG_PREFIX.$(basename $0 .sh)_stdout.$(hostname).log\n\nrun_tar.sh:9:LOG=$TESTLOG_PREFIX.$(basename $0 .sh)_stdout.$(hostname).log\n\nOtherwise, those logs could not be showed up on Maloo.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
